USB Connectors
--------------

There are 2 x **USB HOST** and 1 x **USB DEVICE** (for flashing OS) ports onboard: |USB|, as shown in the figures below.

.. rst-class:: text-center

  |USB2_img|

  *USB 2.0 HOST Port*

  |USBC_img|
  
  *USB Type-C Port*

.. warning::

  Be careful not to touch surrounding electronic components accidentally while plugging USB devices into the embedded IPC version.

:pagebreak:`True`
